gamin: gamin (File Alteration Monitor)
gamin:
gamin: Gamin is a file and directory monitoring system defined to be a
gamin: subset of the FAM (File Alteration Monitor) system. This is a
gamin: service provided by a library which allows to detect when a file or
gamin: a directory has been modified.
